data.description: Mid-century modern living at it's finest! Step through the door to be transported to a Palm Springs vibe with colorful decor and upgrades throughout. Low maintenance cork floors, modern lighting, tall ceilings, tons of natural light, skylights, courtyard facing, and walk-in closets are all features that you have longed for. Storage is not a problem with the over-sized 1-car garage with attached garage cabinets.  Relax on the large back patio finished with pavers and a raised deck. Sip your drink amongst citrus trees and greenery. This 55+ community of Sun City offers 7 Rec Centers, 8 golf courses and a variety of classes and clubs for your active lifestyle. This is what you've been waiting for. Dream living in a community you won't want to leave.
